    "body": "The `spack location -i` command, which works fine without an environment, suddenly stops working when an environment is involved.\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ alias spack\r\nalias spack='spack -e otp-dev-mac'\r\n$ spack location -i maven   # Try with environment\r\n/Users/citibob/spack/otp/var/spack/environments/otp-dev-mac\r\n$ \\spack location -i maven   # Try without environment\r\n/Users/citibob/spack/otp/opt/spack/darwin-highsierra-x86_64/clang-9.0.0-apple/maven-3.5.0-nfxa7a5xs2h3yjjru7muprrgu5u7sonc\r\n```\r\n",
